The provided code chunk is a section of the `__init__` method in the `MayaConverter` class. This class handles file conversions between Maya, Egg, and BAM formats using wxPython for GUI elements. The chunk determines the conversion process based on `convertMode`, initializes necessary processes, sets up a timer to monitor progress, and binds it to an event handler for real-time output updates.

if convertMode == FROM_MAYA_TO_EGG:
            self.convertFromMaya()
        elif convertMode == FROM_BAM_TO_MAYA:
            self.convertToMaya()
        else:
            pass

        self.timer = wx.Timer(self, -1)
        self.Bind(wx.EVT_TIMER, self.onPoll, self.timer)
        self.timer.Start(100)
